	   <div align="left" class="storytitle">The Consolidated Safehouse Vanguard Report (En Francais!)-Part 2</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storyauth">By Nenjin Darkeyes</div>
	   <div align="left" class="storydetail">Jun  9, 2005, 09:08</div>
    
       </td>
       <td align=right valign=top>
      <div align="right" class="newslink"><a class="newslink" href="mailto:?subject=The%20Consolidated%20Safehouse%20Vanguard%20Report%20%28En%20Francais%21%29-Part%202&body=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesafehouse.org%2Farticles%2Freviews%2Farticle_16.php">Email&nbsp;this&nbsp;article</a></div>
